<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/700253-is-this-a-better-read-than-ordinary-grace">Is this a better read than &quot;Ordinary Grace&quot;?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_700253'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F92508.The_Bridge_of_San_Luis_Rey">like</a></span>

