<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/29705852-barbara"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_100x100-6433b08cbe793211f55e184d39e84c4d.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/29705852-barbara">Barbara</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Define &quot;better&quot;. The question needs parameters.<br/>Is a diamond better than a clear emerald? Or is a Van Gogh<br/>better than a Warhol?<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Define "better". The question needs parameters.<br />Is a diamond better than a clear emerald? Or is a Van Gogh<br />better than a Warhol?<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
